body
  .container
    .jumbotron.text-center
      .logo
        a(href="https://sas.utmn.ru")
          img(src="../assets/Logo__blue.png")
      h1 Information about my trips 
      h3 All fields are required
      form(action="/polls/faculty-trips" method="post")
        fieldset
          div(class="input-group")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Name") Name
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Name")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Departure date") Departure date
              input(type="date" required="required" class="form-control" name="Departure date")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Return date") Return date
              input(type="date" required="required" class="form-control" name="Return date")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="The purpose of the trip") The purpose of the trip
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="The purpose of the trip")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Place of destination (country, city)") Place of destination (country, city)
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Place of destination (country, city)")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Specify what mean of transport you will use") Specify what mean of transport you will use: railway, plane, bus, private transport
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Specify what mean of transport you will use")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Specify where you plan to live") Specify where you plan to live: hotel, private apartment 
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Specify where you plan to live")
            .flex-container.row
              input.form-check-input(type="checkbox" required="required"  name="I am aware that I have to be registered at my place")
              label.form-check-label(for="I am aware that I have to be registered at my place") I am aware that I have to be registered at my place of residence within 7 working days and that I am responsible for my registration if I travel around Russia.
            .flex-container.row
              input.form-check-input(type="checkbox" required="required"  name="I am aware that I must bring my documents to the Student Office")
              label.form-check-label(for="I am aware that I must bring my documents to the Student Office") I am aware that I must bring my documents to the Student Office (Room 102) for re-registration within 1-2 working days after my arrival to Tyumen.
            .flex-container.row
              input.form-check-input(type="checkbox" required="required"  name="I am aware of the registration rules")
              label.form-check-label(for="I am aware of the registration rules") I am aware of the registration rules.
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Date of completion") Date of completion
              input(type="date" required="required" class="form-control" name="Date of completion")
            .flex-container.row
              input.form-check-input(type="checkbox" required="required"  name="I agree to the processing of my personal data")
              label.form-check-label(for="I agree to the processing of my personal data") I agree to the processing of my personal data.              
        button(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Submit
